3. Actions that damages or insults others' honor, violating others' intellectual property right, and violating other's rights
4. Hacking or spreading computer virus and constantly sending same advertisement to others who does not want it
5. Illegally using other member's ID 
6. Collecting and saving other user's personal information
7. Impersonating others including EDISON workers and administrator
8. Faking the addresser of sent contents through service
9. Stalking and harassing others
10. Actions that is concerned to disturb service management, and other violations on relevant Act and subordinate statute
